===Wanna try the new...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Gallagher:''' Wanna try the new mix I have? I call it the "Vaporizer"
:{Choice} Will it vaporize me on the spot if I try it?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Will it vaporize me on the spot if I try it?
::'''Gallagher:''' Just one sip of the drink and you get vaporized on the spot? Nah, I can't pull off something like that.
::'''Gallagher:''' But the taste and texture won't let you down
:{Choice} Sounds like a drink that doesn't exist
::'''(Trailblazer):''' "Vaporizer." Sounds like a drink that doesn't exist
::'''Gallagher:''' You know, the way you're describing it actually kinda fits
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 08.png|80px]]
::'''(Trailblazer):''' So, what, I'm going to be drinking air???
::'''Gallagher:''' Hey, scamming guests isn't my style
:'''Gallagher:''' In Penacony, you can find all kinds of drink-mixing ingredients, and sometimes, the flavor that comes out of the mix is hard to describe
:'''Gallagher:''' I don't know how many "unique" drinks I've tasted before the "Vaporizer" was created
:{Choice} Tell me about these unique flavors
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Please tell me about some of these unique flavors
:'''Gallagher:''' There are way too many examples
:'''Gallagher:''' Among recent mixes, "Feast and Exile" and "Masked Talent" can be considered classics. They left me with the deepest impressions
:{Choice} Tell me about "Feast and Exile"
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Tell me about "Feast and Exile"
::'''Gallagher:''' I wanted to mix something lustrous but didn't expect the industrial-grade syrup to be so sweet, dominating all other flavors entirely
::'''Gallagher:''' To rectify that, I added a bit of "bitterness"
::'''Gallagher:''' But I totally didn't expect the supplemental flavors to be that intense... One bite and my old hound soul almost got lost in the utter bitterness
:{Choice} Tell me about "Masked Talent"
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Tell me about "Masked Talent"
::'''Gallagher:''' The original point of the mix was to let people find a bit of sour and sweet amidst the cold shaved ice
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Like finding candy among glass shards?
::'''Gallagher:''' Kinda, but after it went down, it was like drinking a cup of cold water. Nothing sour at all. Boring
:'''Gallagher:''' Comparatively, the "Vaporizer" is doing something really impressive
:'''Gallagher:''' Using SoulGlad as a foundation, and imbued with "Atmo-Sweet" and "Recollection" as supporting ingredients
:'''Gallagher:''' The incongruity woven from both sweet and bitter when you take one sip. It's like you're tasting life itself
:'''Gallagher:''' Every time you try to reminisce and grasp onto something, you're only left with fleeting nothingness
:{Choice} Alright, I'm on my way!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Alright, I'll be there to have a taste of "life"!
:{Choice} This just like me fr!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' This just like me fr! Do I even need to make a special trip for this drink
::'''Gallagher:''' Trust me this once. You won't be disappointed
:'''Gallagher:''' See you at the lounge
}}
